Packed layout record Word has value: u16.

To make bytes, giving owned buffer of u8.
Let bytes be owned buffer of 2 u8 filled with 0.
Let word be Word with value be 42.
Write word into bytes at 0.
Give bytes.

To main, giving i32.
Let bytes be make bytes.
Let word be read Word from bytes at 0.
Give word.value as i32.
